  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个Education GradeSync的完整请求链路图。用户通过Git Client发起HTTPS请求，经过LoadBalancer、NGINX、Workhorse、Puma，最后到Gitaly。关键是中间要有完整的认证流程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Git Client",
        "LoadBalancer",
        "NGINX",
        "Workhorse",
        "Puma",
        "Gitaly"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。确认一下：LoadBalancer到NGINX是HTTP还是HTTPS？以及Education_GradeSync这个标识是加在LoadBalancer到NGINX这一段吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "LoadBalancer",
        "NGINX",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，LoadBalancer到NGINX是HTTP，但头部要带上Education_GradeSync标识。Git Client到LoadBalancer是HTTPS GET /，后面各层都是HTTP GET /传递下去。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Git Client",
        "LoadBalancer",
        "NGINX",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经画出了前向链路：Git Client→LoadBalancer→NGINX→Workhorse→Puma，Puma返回200 OK给Workhorse。现在需要补充Gitaly的交互和认证细节。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Git Client",
        "LoadBalancer",
        "NGINX",
        "Workhorse",
        "Puma",
        "Gitaly"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "认证流程是这样的：Workhorse向Gitaly发起gRPC Request，Gitaly需要验证权限，所以回过来做Auth Verify。然后Workhorse把结果传给Puma确认，Puma返回Auth OK，Workhorse再把这个Auth OK回给Gitaly，最后Gitaly才返回gRPC Response。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Workhorse",
        "Gitaly",
        "Puma",
        "gRPC Request",
        "Auth Verify",
        "Auth Confirm",
        "Auth OK",
        "gRPC Response"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "这里有个细节：Auth Verify是Gitaly主动发给Workhorse的吗？还有Auth Confirm是Workhorse发给Puma的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Gitaly",
        "Workhorse",
        "Puma",
        "Auth Verify",
        "Auth Confirm"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，Gitaly发Auth Verify给Workhorse，Workhorse转发Auth Confirm给Puma，Puma回Auth OK给Workhorse，Workhorse再把Auth OK回给Gitaly。这是一个双向的认证确认过程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Gitaly",
        "Workhorse",
        "Puma",
        "Auth Verify",
        "Auth Confirm",
        "Auth OK"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成了。整个链路包括：Git Client经LoadBalancer、NGINX、Workhorse、Puma到Gitaly的gRPC调用，中间的Auth Verify→Auth Confirm→Auth OK→Auth OK的双向认证，最后响应逐层返回。所有异步和同步消息都用对了箭头类型。",
